headline: Robinhood Stock Keeps Surging to New Highs
summary: Robinhood (HOOD) shows strong technical momentum, hitting a new 52-week high on Wednesday, June 25. HOOD has a 100% technical “Buy” signal via Barchart. Shares are up more than 270% over the past 52 weeks and have more than doubled in the year to date. Fundamentals reveal robust revenue growth...
